title: Canada election does not affect decision on Keystone pipeline: Kerry
text:
Canada election does not affect decis... Canada election does not affect decision on Keystone pipeline: Kerry There are 2 comments on the Reuters story from 10 hrs ago, titled Canada election does not affect decision on Keystone pipeline: Kerry . In it, Reuters reports that: 
U.S. Secretary of State John Kerry said Tuesday that the ousting of the ruling Conservative Party in Canada's election will not affect his decision on whether to approve the controversial Keystone XL pipeline between the two countries. Election victor Justin Trudeau of the Liberal party has said he would repair Canada's relations with the Obama administration and take stronger measures against climate change.
